    if (abs(min(top[,x])) < abs(max(top[,x]))) y = ((-10:11)*2-1)/(2*10/(abs(max(top[,x])))) 
    else  y = ((-10:11)*2-1)/(2*10/(abs(min(top[,x]))))
    if (abs(min(top[,x])) ==0 && abs(max(top[,x])) ==0) y=10
